---
name: Google Search Minimal Test
description: Minimal prompt to call internal google_search via function tool
version: 1.0.0

inputs:
  query:
    description: Search query string
    type: string
    default: "Yoco company overview payments South Africa"

model:
  api: responses
  configuration:
    connection: openai_conn
    model: gpt-5-mini
    type: pom-llm-proxy
    tools:
      - type: function
        function:
          name: google_search
          description: Execute Google search
          parameters:
            type: object
            properties:
              query:
                type: string
              num_results:
                type: integer
                default: 5
              language:
                type: string
                default: "en"
              country:
                type: string
                default: "za"
            required: ["query"]
  parameters:
    max_tokens: 200

processing_config:
  source_collection: Domain

---

system:
Call google_search exactly once with:
- query: "{{ query }}"
- num_results: 5
- language: "en"
- country: "za"

Then list the top 3 result titles and URLs on separate lines.
If no results, say "No results".

user:
Call google_search and show top 3 results.
